article.description: — Tim Finke tallied 13 points and 11 rebounds to carry Wright St. to a 71-47 win over Miami (Ohio) on Saturday.
article.headline: Finke leads Wright State over Miami (Ohio) 71-47
article.linkText: Finke leads Wright State over Miami (Ohio) 71-47
article.story: DAYTON, Ohio -- — Tim Finke tallied 13 points and 11 rebounds to carry Wright St. to a 71-47 win over Miami (Ohio) on Saturday. Trey Calvin had 16 points for Wright St. (1-1). Grant Basile added 14 points and three blocks. Loudon Love had 11 points. Dalonte Brown had seven rebounds for the RedHawks (1-1). Dae Dae Grant, the RedHawks’ leading scorer heading into the contest at 21.0 points per game, scored three points on 1-of-12 shooting. Mekhi Lairy, whose 14.0 points per game entering the contest ranked second on the RedHawks, failed to make a shot from the floor (0 of 7). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
